title: War of the Roses: That's a Girl's Name?
description: Caitlin's boyfriend Alex has been going into work earlier because he's been giving his co-worker a ride in. Caitlin didn't think anything of it until she heard Alex voice-to-texting this co-worker something inappropriate.  Now she is wondering if this work relationship is platonic or not.
